title: Stress - Stress - 1991 Psychedellic Rock Band
description:
Stress were a psychedelic rock band from 1991. Their  contemporaries would be bands like Lenny Kravitz, 24-7 Spyz, King's X, Defunkt, The Veldt, Terence Trent D'Arby, and Basehead. Stress was more psychedelic and Beatlesque in their lyrics and the melodies of the songs, which could easily stay in people's minds. 

1. Indian Summers Dream
2. Flowers In The Rain
3. Rosechild
4. Innocent World
5. Daytime Believer
6. Beautiful People
7. My Father Once Said
8. Together
9. Lordy Lord
10. Red Sun
